  "prompt": "Which is the best sports bra?",
  "response": "The \"best\" sports bra can vary depending on individual needs and preferences, such as the level of impact during your activity, your breast size, and personal comfort. However, some highly-rated sports bras that are popular among athletes and fitness enthusiasts include:\n\n1. **Lululemon Enlite Front Zip Bra** - Known for its excellent support and comfort, this bra is ideal for high-impact activities. It features a front zip for easy wear and removal.\n\n2. **Nike Pro Indy Bra** - This bra is praised for its versatility and comfort, suitable for medium-impact activities. It offers removable pads and a wide band for added support.\n\n3. **Under Armour Infinity High Sports Bra** - Designed for high-impact activities, this bra offers maximum support and a unique cross-back design for a secure fit.\n\n4. **Brooks Dare Crossback Run Bra** - Highly recommended for runners, this bra provides excellent support and features adjustable straps and a smooth, chafe-free band.\n\n5. **Shefit Ultimate Sports Bra** - Known for its customizable fit, this bra is ideal for larger cup sizes and high-impact activities. It features a unique Velcro closure system for adjustable support.\n\nWhen choosing a sports bra, consider factors such as the level of impact of your activity, your breast size, and any specific features you need, such as moisture-wicking fabric or adjustable straps. It's also helpful to read reviews and possibly try a few different brands to find the one that works best for you.",
